Deployment Preparation & Staging Environment Setup

Key Steps:

Hosting Platform Setup: Deploy to Vercel (recommended) or Netlify.

Environment Variable Configuration: Secure API keys and credentials using .env files.

Deploy to Staging: Validate deployment and test application behavior.

Staging Environment Testing:

Functional Testing: Verify product listing, search, and checkout.

Performance Testing: Use Lighthouse or GTmetrix.

Security Testing: Validate API security, HTTPS usage, and input validation.

